name: Human skin cell atlas
desc: Integrated healthy adult and embryonic skin scRNA-seq data

name: Human adult healthy 10x data
desc: A scRNA-seq dataset containing human healthy adult skin scRNA-seq data stratified by dermal and epidermal compartments (10x; n=5 , k=200,463). Healthy adulty skin 10x scRNA-seq data - E-MTAB-8142.

name: Human adult healthy, psoriasis, atopic dermatitis 10x data
Human fetal 10x data
desc: A scRNA-seq dataset containing human fetal skin scRNA-seq data stratified by dermal and epidermal compartments (10x; n=7, k=43,432). Fetal skin 10x scRNA-seq data - E-MTAB-8142.

name: Human adult Smart-seq2 data
desc: A SS2 scRNA-seq dataset containing healthy human adult skin SS2 scRNA-seq data stratified by FACs sorted cell-states (SS2; n=5, k=1,807). Healthy Adult Skin SS2 scRNA-seq data - E-MTAB-8142.
